1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,819
Congratulations, you have completed the final challenge.

2
00:00:02,819 --> 00:00:07,379
Challenge by challenge, you have been building a pyramid measured not in height or stone,

3
00:00:07,379 --> 00:00:11,640
but in coordination, communication, and a shared goal.

4
00:00:11,640 --> 00:00:14,640
None of this would have been possible individually.

5
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:21,280
It was teamwork, your ability to listen to one another and adapt, that allowed you to move forward and reach this point.

6
00:00:21,280 --> 00:00:23,739
As in the great constructions of history,

7
00:00:23,739 --> 00:00:26,100
every contribution was necessary.

8
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:28,399
You have shown that by working together,

9
00:00:28,399 --> 00:00:30,399
you can go very far.

10
00:00:30,399 --> 00:00:32,799
Congratulations on the teamwork you have shown.
